    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"422543\">@Stuart Presnell</span> I was going in that direction:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">mayLeft</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">cop.coords</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.cube.moves.l.top</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.target</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">mayUp</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">cop.coords</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.cube.moves.u.top</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.target</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">mayRight</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">cop.coords</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.cube.moves.r.top</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.target</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">mayDown</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">cop.coords</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.cube.moves.d.top</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.target</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">goLeft</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.mayLeft</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">let</span> <span class=\"n\">newCoords</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop.coords.fst</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.coords.snd</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">let</span> <span class=\"n\">newCube</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.cube.moves.l</span>\n  <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">goUp</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.mayUp</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">goRight</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.mayRight</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">goDown</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">cop.mayDown</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">CuOnPa</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Then I'd say that a path would be a sequence of applications of those <code>goUp, ...</code> functions and a solution would be a path that would take me to the winning state. But I got stuck because of the hypotheses <code>h</code> that they need. How'd you formalize such path?</p>",
        "id": 269868748,
        "sender_full_name": "Arthur Paulino",
        "timestamp": 1643468139
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>More generally, how to formalize a path that's valid?</p>",
        "id": 269868947,
        "sender_full_name": "Arthur Paulino",
        "timestamp": 1643468382
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(I think I saw the solution just by talking it out <span aria-label=\"open mouth\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f62e\" role=\"img\" title=\"open mouth\">:open_mouth:</span> )</p>",
        "id": 269869055,
        "sender_full_name": "Arthur Paulino",
        "timestamp": 1643468423
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The issue is that I'm constraining consistency in my structure. Instead, I should allow the instantiation of invalid states have validity check as a prop, then require that every state in the path obeys to it</p>",
        "id": 269869293,
        "sender_full_name": "Arthur Paulino",
        "timestamp": 1643468667
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>So you could (lazily) build a tree with the starting state as root and the available moves as branches, and then search the tree for a path to a solved state, pruning branches that correspond to invalid moves.</p>",
        "id": 269869745,
        "sender_full_name": "Stuart Presnell",
        "timestamp": 1643469181
    }
]